### Basic delegation: list Customers from Northwind V4
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Customers?$top=5

### $filter + $orderby — forwarded to Northwind. Plugin translates the
### local field names (`country`) back to the remote shape (`Country`)
### automatically via the consumption view's `as` clauses.
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Customers?$filter=country eq 'Germany'&$orderby=companyName

### $select — only the listed columns are projected, saving bandwidth
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Customers?$top=3&$select=customerId,companyName,city

### $count — Northwind returns total count alongside the top page
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Customers?$top=3&$count=true

### Point read by key (CustomerID is a 5-char string in Northwind)
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Customers('ALFKI')
